<document>

    <properties>
        <title>Apache James Server 3 - WebAdmin Configuration</title>
    </properties>

    <body>

        <section name="WebAdmin configuration">

            <p><a href="manage-webadmin">WebAdmin</a> is a REST API allowing to manage James when using Guice wirings.</p>

            <subsection name="webadmin.properties">

                <p>Consult <a href="https://github.com/apache/james-project/blob/master/dockerfiles/run/guice/cassandra/destination/conf/webadmin.properties">tika.properties</a> in GIT to get some examples and hints.</p>

                <br/>

                <dl>
                    <dt><strong>enabled</strong></dt>
                    <dd>true/false. Governs whether WebAdmin should be enabled</dd>

                    <dt><strong>port</strong></dt>
                    <dd>Port the server listens on</dd>

                    <dt><strong>https.enabled</strong></dt>
                    <dd>true/false. Should HTTPS be enabled? Defaults to false.</dd>

                    <dt><strong>https.keystore</strong></dt>
                    <dd>Keystore to be used to create secure connections.</dd>

                    <dt><strong>https.password</strong></dt>
                    <dd>Password to unlock keystore</dd>

                    <dt><strong>https.trust.keystore</strong></dt>
                    <dd>Self signed keystores only. Keystore to be used as certification authority.</dd>

                    <dt><strong>https.trust.password</strong></dt>
                    <dd>Self signed keystores only. Password to unlock trust keystore.</dd>

                    <dt><strong>jwt.enabled</strong></dt>
                    <dd>true/false. Should JWT be used to secure this API?</dd>

                    <dt><strong>cors.enable</strong></dt>
                    <dd>true/false. Defaults to false. Should CORS requests be allowed?</dd>

                    <dt><strong>cors.origin</strong></dt>
                    <dd>Which origins to allow for CORS requests?</dd>
                </dl>

            </subsection>

        </section>

    </body>

</document>
